>> *Calls from landlines are typically charged between 2p and 10p per minute
while calls from mobiles typically cost between 10p and 40p per minute. Calls
from landlines and mobiles should be included in free call packages. Calls may
be recorded for quality and training purposes. If a Diabetes UK member of
staff or volunteer has concerns about your own or someone else’s safety and
well-being, the concern may be reported to the Diabetes UK Safeguarding Team
